WEBVTT

01:46.040 --> 01:47.720
The rain is bound to fall.

01:47.800 --> 01:49.640
I'm bound to be wed.

01:50.160 --> 01:51.680
Trees are ready to bloom.

01:52.200 --> 01:53.760
I'm ready to be married.

01:54.280 --> 01:56.160
Flowers long to bear fruit.

01:56.240 --> 01:57.400
TALES OF A MORTAL DREAM

01:57.480 --> 01:58.480
I long to be married.

01:58.560 --> 02:00.640
SU JIAN

02:02.440 --> 02:05.440
Is this the Little Pomegranate
from the painting?

02:08.000 --> 02:09.520
So we are in…

02:11.400 --> 02:12.640
I was just thinking.

02:13.560 --> 02:16.240
This painting must carry
the artist's memories and emotions.

02:17.200 --> 02:20.400
Maybe I could try
the spell Master left me,

02:20.480 --> 02:22.560
like entering the Star Stone illusion.

02:22.640 --> 02:24.000
I didn't expect it to actually work.

02:24.600 --> 02:27.000
Cui Jun is good-looking.

02:27.520 --> 02:29.840
We've known each other since childhood
and have been betrothed before birth.

02:29.920 --> 02:31.600
Cui Jun…

02:31.680 --> 02:35.200
The painter is Cui… Cui Jun?

02:35.960 --> 02:38.160
The one who painted this.
But I've always treated him

02:38.240 --> 02:39.960
like a younger brother.

02:40.040 --> 02:43.120
How can anyone marry their own brother?

02:43.200 --> 02:46.480
Does that make any sense?
Is that even reasonable?

02:47.000 --> 02:49.240
A forced melon is never sweet.

02:49.760 --> 02:50.720
Better let it rot

02:52.440 --> 02:54.040
on the vine.

02:56.920 --> 02:59.400
When will I ever have

02:59.480 --> 03:02.840
a love like in the stories?

03:03.400 --> 03:04.880
He chases, I run.

03:04.960 --> 03:06.760
I tease, he laughs.

03:06.840 --> 03:09.040
I faint, and he kisses me.

03:09.120 --> 03:10.920
How beautiful that must be.

03:13.720 --> 03:15.840
Oh, tree.

03:19.960 --> 03:23.680
Will there be an attractive,
interesting man

03:23.760 --> 03:24.760
who falls in love with me?

03:25.480 --> 03:28.320
If the answer is yes, stay silent

03:29.040 --> 03:30.200
and don't move, alright?

03:49.080 --> 03:50.360
Handsome,

03:51.560 --> 03:52.880
who are you?

03:53.600 --> 03:55.560
You could get arrested

03:56.600 --> 03:58.400
for breaking into someone's home.

04:01.280 --> 04:02.560
I'm kind.

04:02.640 --> 04:03.560
I won't make a fuss over this.

04:03.640 --> 04:04.960
You should leave now.

04:05.560 --> 04:06.800
If fate allows,

04:06.880 --> 04:08.680
we may meet again someday.

04:09.760 --> 04:11.280
Go on.

04:11.360 --> 04:13.360
Hurry and leave.

04:14.120 --> 04:16.880
Don't get too mesmerized
by my beauty, alright?

04:20.079 --> 04:21.240
Not leaving?

04:24.240 --> 04:26.040
So you want to stay and have a chat?

04:43.040 --> 04:44.200
Sir,

04:44.720 --> 04:46.920
sneaking up behind a lady

04:47.000 --> 04:49.160
and eavesdropping on her

04:49.240 --> 04:50.240
is a no-no.

04:50.320 --> 04:51.480
A little naughty.

04:53.160 --> 04:54.120
Tell me.

04:54.200 --> 04:56.840
From which line did you start listening?

04:57.440 --> 04:59.800
Was it "He chases, I run,"

04:59.880 --> 05:02.400
or "I faint, and he kisses me?"

05:09.640 --> 05:11.800
The way you greet people is rather unique.

05:11.880 --> 05:15.280
You've definitely caught my attention.

05:16.720 --> 05:17.680
I'm Su Jian.

05:17.760 --> 05:19.320
What's your name?

05:19.400 --> 05:20.880
Where do you live?

05:20.960 --> 05:21.800
How old are you?

05:21.880 --> 05:23.120
Are you married?

05:23.200 --> 05:24.560
Have you picked names
for our children yet?

05:25.840 --> 05:26.760
You're tired?

05:27.960 --> 05:29.640
The sky is still bright.

05:30.640 --> 05:32.080
No rush.

05:32.160 --> 05:33.320
How do I undo this?

05:33.840 --> 05:35.480
How… Help me.

05:36.160 --> 05:37.400
Sir.

05:38.360 --> 05:39.960
Why won't you speak?

05:40.640 --> 05:42.720
I often come to this weaving house,

05:42.800 --> 05:44.600
but I've never seen you before.

05:49.560 --> 05:50.560
Where are you going?

05:50.640 --> 05:52.600
It's raining outside.

05:52.680 --> 05:54.040
For a handsome man like you,

05:54.120 --> 05:55.600
if your clothes get soaked,

05:55.680 --> 05:57.280
you should take them off immediately

05:59.520 --> 06:00.720
and dry them

06:01.400 --> 06:02.880
or you'll fall ill.

06:07.320 --> 06:08.240
So it's true.

06:09.320 --> 06:10.720
Han Ba can't speak.

06:12.720 --> 06:14.120
<i>Wangyan.</i>

06:15.560 --> 06:16.400
Wangyan.

06:17.320 --> 06:18.360
Jian.

06:23.240 --> 06:25.200
Si Feng once told me

06:26.160 --> 06:29.400
I had carried out a mission alone
involving Han Ba.

06:30.400 --> 06:31.600
Could this be that mission?

06:32.640 --> 06:33.680
Mission?

06:35.200 --> 06:37.280
Disguising yourself as Su Jian's sister?

06:40.520 --> 06:42.280
Looks like you've cast the Word Magic

06:42.360 --> 06:43.760
over the entire Su family.

06:44.400 --> 06:46.240
Su Jian really believes you're her sister.

06:47.760 --> 06:49.920
Wangyan, you made iced treats again?

06:50.000 --> 06:52.040
How can you make ice treats in any season?

06:52.680 --> 06:54.880
Do you know magic?

06:54.960 --> 06:58.840
You must be the fairy from the stories.

06:59.360 --> 07:00.640
Is it good?

07:00.720 --> 07:02.160
I remember you once said

07:02.240 --> 07:04.600
you liked making iced treats for Lu Wuyi.

07:05.160 --> 07:06.040
It seems

07:06.640 --> 07:09.680
you've brought your real habits
into the mission.

07:10.520 --> 07:12.320
Aren't you afraid of exposing yourself?

07:12.400 --> 07:16.880
You must've known I was troubled,

07:16.960 --> 07:20.000
so you made these iced treats
to comfort me.

07:21.600 --> 07:23.280
What are you talking about?

07:23.360 --> 07:24.680
Lotus seeds.

07:25.560 --> 07:27.480
I'm as pitiful as these lotus seeds.

07:27.560 --> 07:31.360
My heart is like these iced lotus seeds.

07:31.440 --> 07:34.400
Col' an' bitter…

07:34.480 --> 07:35.920
Are you speaking in tongues?

07:36.000 --> 07:37.880
Cold

07:37.960 --> 07:39.840
and bitter.

07:41.480 --> 07:43.040
I know what you mean.

07:43.640 --> 07:45.000
It's been a whole month,

07:45.520 --> 07:48.160
and you're still not over that mute man?

07:48.240 --> 07:51.440
What? Mute?

07:51.520 --> 07:53.960
Wangyan, you're so ugly,
but why do you speak so…

07:54.760 --> 07:58.560
I mean, you're so pretty,
but why do you speak harshly?

07:58.640 --> 08:01.480
He's just steady and quiet.

08:02.000 --> 08:03.520
He complements me.

08:03.600 --> 08:04.840
Is he good-looking?

08:05.440 --> 08:06.480
Of course.

08:06.560 --> 08:07.800
Indeed, you complement each other.

08:09.840 --> 08:10.760
That's an insult.

08:10.840 --> 08:13.360
You really deserve a scolding.

08:13.440 --> 08:14.280
Do you remember

08:14.360 --> 08:16.440
you're supposed to marry Jun
in three months?

08:17.040 --> 08:18.120
Jun?

08:18.200 --> 08:19.280
Who is that?

08:19.360 --> 08:20.520
Chenjun?

08:21.120 --> 08:22.040
Cui Jun.

08:24.680 --> 08:27.160
I don't want to marry him anymore.

08:31.080 --> 08:33.679
Cold and bitter.

08:35.280 --> 08:37.679
You're here brooding over it,

08:37.760 --> 08:39.520
while he can't even

08:39.600 --> 08:41.000
be bothered with you.

08:44.800 --> 08:46.480
They say in stories

08:46.560 --> 08:48.680
that when a woman pursues a man,
it's like a thin veil between them.

08:48.760 --> 08:51.400
I've even gone as far
as the barn next door.

08:52.000 --> 08:53.080
I refuse to believe

08:53.600 --> 08:54.920
I can't tear through this thin veil.

08:56.120 --> 08:57.120
Wangyan,

08:57.640 --> 08:59.160
just watch me.

09:05.680 --> 09:06.720
Wangyan.

09:07.600 --> 09:08.760
I choked myself.

09:12.200 --> 09:15.040
If you still won't speak,

09:15.120 --> 09:18.760
I'll show you what a fierce woman is like.

09:23.640 --> 09:25.880
Fine. I'll smash my head
right here and die.

09:26.480 --> 09:29.200
Let's see if you'll call
a physician for me then.

09:55.560 --> 09:56.920
This is a gift for you.

09:57.000 --> 09:58.240
You've barely passed 20.

09:58.320 --> 10:00.680
It's the perfect age
to carry an old man's fan.

10:01.280 --> 10:03.200
Honestly, I was worried
you're too handsome,

10:03.280 --> 10:05.240
and other girls might start eyeing you.

10:06.040 --> 10:08.680
This old man's fan will do just the trick.

10:08.760 --> 10:12.720
It'll make your lofty, noble charm
a little questionable

10:13.320 --> 10:15.840
and make you less appealing
to other women.

10:19.240 --> 10:20.720
I've given you a gift.

10:20.800 --> 10:22.240
Won't you at least say thank you?

10:32.800 --> 10:34.120
My name is Su Jian.

10:34.200 --> 10:35.160
What's yours?

10:41.480 --> 10:44.400
You won't even tell me your name?

10:44.480 --> 10:47.120
If I don't know your name,

10:47.200 --> 10:48.760
how am I supposed
to match our birth charts

10:48.840 --> 10:51.720
and figure out when we'll get married?

11:05.760 --> 11:08.080
Do I look pretty today?

11:09.160 --> 11:10.480
What a delicate flower.

11:10.560 --> 11:12.160
If you don't pick it now,

11:13.000 --> 11:14.080
it might belong

11:16.760 --> 11:18.360
to another man tomorrow.

11:19.000 --> 11:20.000
I…

12:19.800 --> 12:21.880
You always manage to find me.

12:24.400 --> 12:26.600
You always hide in the dark.

12:26.680 --> 12:28.440
Of course, no one else can see you.

12:30.240 --> 12:31.480
But I can.

12:31.560 --> 12:32.880
But I can.

12:33.560 --> 12:34.400
My heart.

12:35.320 --> 12:36.840
My heart.

12:36.920 --> 12:38.880
Can feel you are here.

12:52.040 --> 12:53.240
I remember everything now.

12:58.720 --> 13:00.280
But in my memory,

13:01.640 --> 13:03.640
I was saying that to someone else.

13:04.240 --> 13:05.240
Wangyan,

13:06.200 --> 13:07.240
thank you.

13:07.320 --> 13:09.040
You're the only one who can see me.

13:09.920 --> 13:12.000
You always hide in the dark.

13:12.520 --> 13:14.720
Of course no one else can see you,

13:16.440 --> 13:17.640
but I can.

13:18.600 --> 13:19.640
My heart

13:20.960 --> 13:23.000
can feel you're here.

13:28.240 --> 13:29.800
Is it Lu Wuyi?

13:37.720 --> 13:39.320
There's no moon tonight.

13:42.560 --> 13:44.040
The moon is always there.

13:44.640 --> 13:47.440
It's just being mischievous tonight.

13:47.520 --> 13:48.720
It's hiding.

13:49.600 --> 13:52.040
The moon is meant to shine,

13:52.120 --> 13:54.040
to be admired, to be written into poems,

13:54.760 --> 13:56.400
to carry people's longing and praise.

13:57.040 --> 13:59.920
But tonight, no one can see it.

14:01.440 --> 14:02.680
Will it feel sad?

14:04.800 --> 14:06.000
Dear,

14:07.400 --> 14:08.480
are you talking about yourself?

14:15.760 --> 14:17.480
I am sad.

14:18.640 --> 14:19.480
Wangyan,

14:20.440 --> 14:21.560
you were right.

14:21.640 --> 14:23.600
It's always just been me.

14:24.200 --> 14:26.280
He's never responded to me.

14:26.960 --> 14:29.040
He wouldn't even tell me his name.

14:31.160 --> 14:32.320
He doesn't love you.

14:34.120 --> 14:36.640
But Cui Jun does. And I love you too.

14:38.560 --> 14:40.160
To me,

14:40.240 --> 14:42.440
you're the most important person.

14:43.440 --> 14:45.160
I'll stay with you forever.

14:46.800 --> 14:47.840
Jian,

14:48.800 --> 14:49.960
sleep.

14:50.680 --> 14:51.880
Have a good dream.

14:52.400 --> 14:54.120
When the dream ends,

14:55.040 --> 14:57.040
I'll wake you.

14:59.480 --> 15:00.920
And if I don't,

15:02.480 --> 15:04.320
don't ever wake up.

15:13.160 --> 15:15.520
Han Ba still refuses to speak.

15:16.640 --> 15:17.680
Jian,

15:18.800 --> 15:19.760
I'm sorry to put you through this.

15:33.720 --> 15:34.840
Wait.

15:39.800 --> 15:42.920
Are you the quiet man my sister likes?

15:47.760 --> 15:50.240
She suddenly fell ill
and has been unconscious.

15:50.320 --> 15:52.160
The physician said
it's a matter of the heart.

15:52.240 --> 15:54.640
Only the voice of the one
she loves can bring her back.

16:07.520 --> 16:09.720
I don't have a human name.

16:10.640 --> 16:12.120
I only have a demon name.

16:14.640 --> 16:15.800
I'm Han Ba.

16:16.640 --> 16:17.760
And

16:18.280 --> 16:20.360
the moment I speak,

16:21.000 --> 16:23.640
drought will fall upon the world.

16:25.720 --> 16:27.960
I've lived inside a tree.

16:28.960 --> 16:30.320
Day after day,

16:31.200 --> 16:32.400
I was so bored.

16:33.680 --> 16:35.640
No one ever spoke to me

16:37.040 --> 16:38.360
until I met you.

16:38.880 --> 16:40.520
Oh, tree.

16:40.600 --> 16:43.200
Will there be
an attractive, interesting man

16:43.280 --> 16:46.520
who falls in love with me?
If the answer is yes,

16:46.600 --> 16:49.240
stay silent

16:50.640 --> 16:51.720
and don't move, alright?

17:03.240 --> 17:04.560
Meeting you

17:05.680 --> 17:08.560
was like a flame melting ice.

17:09.319 --> 17:11.720
This world that was once indifferent to me

17:15.599 --> 17:18.079
suddenly came alive.

17:22.359 --> 17:24.040
Even if I couldn't speak,

17:24.119 --> 17:25.960
just watching you talk

17:27.079 --> 17:28.480
made me happy.

17:32.600 --> 17:34.440
I wanted to answer you.

17:35.320 --> 17:37.520
I wanted to tell you

17:37.600 --> 17:39.440
everything I felt.

17:40.520 --> 17:41.680
But

17:42.440 --> 17:44.680
if I ever responded to your love,

17:45.480 --> 17:46.960
everyone you cherish in this world

17:48.240 --> 17:49.680
would be destroyed by me.

17:55.360 --> 17:57.400
You like stories, don't you?

17:59.040 --> 18:00.280
Stop sleeping.

18:01.320 --> 18:02.600
I'll tell you a story.

18:04.360 --> 18:05.560
Wake up,

18:07.320 --> 18:08.320
alright?

18:23.640 --> 18:24.800
It works.

18:29.320 --> 18:30.560
Jian,

18:30.640 --> 18:32.720
did you hear the voice
of the man you love?

18:34.760 --> 18:36.240
The dream is over.

18:37.280 --> 18:38.760
Wake up now.

18:48.560 --> 18:49.800
As expected.

18:49.880 --> 18:52.880
Only the one she loves could wake her.

18:56.760 --> 18:57.720
This is bad!

18:57.800 --> 18:59.120
-This is bad!
-Quiet.

18:59.200 --> 19:00.160
Something's happened!

19:00.240 --> 19:03.200
Su Jian, why are you still here?
You should go take a look.

19:03.280 --> 19:06.320
Your mother fought someone over water
and was beaten to death.

19:16.680 --> 19:18.160
What was my mission

19:20.200 --> 19:21.440
back then?

19:22.600 --> 19:24.440
Wu Wangyan's mission

19:24.520 --> 19:27.400
was to capture the water demons
hiding in the underground waterways

19:27.480 --> 19:28.880
of Luo'an.

19:29.480 --> 19:30.680
But what does that have to do

19:30.760 --> 19:32.480
with making you speak?

19:33.080 --> 19:34.320
Aren't you supposed to be smart?

19:36.000 --> 19:36.840
Can't you figure that out?

19:36.920 --> 19:38.280
Of course I can.

19:38.360 --> 19:39.880
I just want to hear you say it.

19:41.200 --> 19:42.960
If she wanted to flush out
the water demons,

19:44.280 --> 19:46.720
she had to make Han Ba speak,
which would trigger a drought,

19:47.680 --> 19:50.280
dry up water sources,
and force the water demons

19:50.360 --> 19:53.000
out of the tangled underground waterways.

19:53.680 --> 19:55.280
There's no way

19:56.120 --> 19:58.760
I would've agreed
to cause such devastation.

19:59.360 --> 20:01.600
That's why Jiu Ying erased my memory.

20:05.520 --> 20:07.880
Drought brings conflict and unrest.

20:08.840 --> 20:11.000
As fear and hatred multiply,

20:11.080 --> 20:12.760
Jiu Ying feeds on them

20:12.840 --> 20:14.800
and becomes stronger.

20:16.320 --> 20:17.680
I didn't understand back then.

20:19.400 --> 20:21.240
Now I do.

20:22.160 --> 20:24.920
That was Jiu Ying's true intention.

20:31.480 --> 20:32.640
<i>If I didn't speak,</i>

20:33.200 --> 20:34.480
<i>I couldn't save her.</i>

20:36.400 --> 20:37.520
<i>But if I did,</i>

20:38.040 --> 20:39.480
<i>I harmed her</i>

20:40.360 --> 20:42.080
<i>and the entire mortal world.</i>

20:45.360 --> 20:46.840
I don't have a mother anymore.

20:57.040 --> 20:59.120
<i>I know my sins run deep,</i>

20:59.200 --> 21:01.040
<i>but I never dared tell her the truth.</i>

21:02.240 --> 21:03.520
<i>Not until</i>

21:03.600 --> 21:05.880
<i>the double-flower hunter</i>
<i>came to bring me to justice.</i>

21:14.360 --> 21:15.240
Han Ba,

21:15.840 --> 21:18.840
you've acted recklessly
and brought drought upon the land,

21:18.920 --> 21:21.160
turning Luo'an into scorched earth,

21:21.240 --> 21:23.000
leaving countless lives in ruin.

21:23.080 --> 21:25.120
By the order of Master Chi Wen,

21:25.200 --> 21:27.040
we're here to take you back
to the Shilin Sect to face judgment.

21:27.120 --> 21:28.160
You'd better not try something silly.

21:28.240 --> 21:30.400
My martial senior is very powerful.

21:32.800 --> 21:33.680
He's getting away.

21:34.960 --> 21:36.480
-I shouldn't have changed my mind
-Si Feng!

21:36.560 --> 21:38.040
and brought a reckless fool
like you along.

21:38.120 --> 21:39.800
-Wait outside.
-Si Feng!

21:40.360 --> 21:41.680
Si Feng! Si Feng!

21:42.400 --> 21:43.480
Wait for me.

21:44.000 --> 21:46.360
I'll soon become
a powerful double-flower hunter.

21:46.880 --> 21:48.960
Si Feng, I finally found you.

21:49.040 --> 21:50.200
Careful!

21:50.280 --> 21:51.400
Careful of what?

21:53.480 --> 21:54.680
-I don't want to hurt you.
-Stand aside.

21:55.600 --> 21:57.000
I wanted to.

21:57.080 --> 21:58.000
You!

22:02.600 --> 22:04.360
Si Feng, he's got backup.

22:04.960 --> 22:07.200
Anyway, two against two. It's even.

22:08.800 --> 22:10.240
Can you even beat her?

22:10.320 --> 22:13.840
She's a thousand-year-old nine-tailed fox
from the Formless Moon Sect.

22:13.920 --> 22:14.760
She's a fox demon?

22:15.680 --> 22:18.680
The double-flower hunter
from the Shilin Sect is quite heartless.

22:19.320 --> 22:20.960
How can you bring yourself

22:21.040 --> 22:22.880
to tear apart a couple in love?

22:24.360 --> 22:25.200
How amusing.

22:25.880 --> 22:27.640
A fox demon from the Formless Moon Sect

22:28.240 --> 22:29.880
lecturing me on human sentiment?

22:30.880 --> 22:32.040
What are you doing here?

22:32.800 --> 22:35.480
I'm here to rid the world of water demons.

22:36.120 --> 22:38.480
Whether your sect
creates evil or destroys it,

22:39.080 --> 22:40.160
can you really tell the difference?

22:41.800 --> 22:42.840
No matter what,

22:43.640 --> 22:45.560
I won't let you take Han Ba away.

22:46.600 --> 22:47.600
The fault isn't his.

22:48.200 --> 22:49.400
He's innocent.

22:49.920 --> 22:51.080
Of course it isn't his fault.

22:51.160 --> 22:52.240
It's yours.

22:52.320 --> 22:54.560
You're the one who made him speak.
You wretched fox.

22:54.640 --> 22:55.960
Don't think you can hide what you did.

22:56.560 --> 22:59.040
I've never sparred with a fox
from the Formless Moon Sect.

22:59.120 --> 23:01.400
Today is the perfect chance.

23:01.480 --> 23:02.920
I've never fought alongside you, Si Feng.

23:03.000 --> 23:05.200
Time to show what I can do.

23:06.240 --> 23:07.280
Wait.

23:09.200 --> 23:11.440
The drought was indeed caused by me.

23:12.440 --> 23:14.960
I'll return to the Shilin Sect with you.

23:16.240 --> 23:17.320
But

23:17.920 --> 23:19.680
let me see her one last time

23:21.720 --> 23:23.360
and bid farewell to her.

23:24.040 --> 23:25.360
Please.

23:35.000 --> 23:37.480
So you are a demon.

23:39.200 --> 23:41.400
Why did you cause the drought?

23:43.920 --> 23:48.160
The drought killed my mother.

24:09.600 --> 24:11.200
I'll explain everything to Su Jian.

24:12.360 --> 24:13.800
It's not what she thinks.

24:15.560 --> 24:16.640
-It was me.
-No need.

24:17.600 --> 24:19.360
I've hurt her enough.

24:21.800 --> 24:23.560
I can't let her know

24:25.360 --> 24:27.320
that the sister she loves
was using her all along.

24:28.800 --> 24:33.320
Does the Formless Moon Sect
have Word Magic that can alter memories?

24:35.280 --> 24:37.000
Can you make her forget me?

24:39.520 --> 24:43.680
Fairy, aren't your spells powerful?

24:44.520 --> 24:46.080
Can you make me forget him?

24:49.000 --> 24:50.240
Please.

25:25.080 --> 25:26.080
What?

25:26.160 --> 25:27.640
Can't bring yourself to do it?

25:28.680 --> 25:30.400
It's just

25:30.920 --> 25:32.600
their love is rare,

25:33.120 --> 25:34.840
like a precious treasure.

25:35.440 --> 25:36.600
I can't bear to destroy it.

25:43.680 --> 25:46.360
If you can't, use this.

26:12.280 --> 26:13.800
You've got the softest heart

26:14.480 --> 26:15.640
of any fox I've met.

26:17.480 --> 26:19.080
You left a hope

26:19.920 --> 26:21.240
for Su Jian and Han Ba.

26:35.880 --> 26:37.600
After Su Jian forgot me,

26:37.680 --> 26:40.880
I was ready to return to the Shilin Sect
to accept punishment and end the drought.

26:41.760 --> 26:43.080
<i>But I never expected</i>

26:43.600 --> 26:44.720
<i>Su Jian</i>

26:45.240 --> 26:48.120
<i>to seek revenge on the man</i>
<i>who killed her mother.</i>

26:49.680 --> 26:51.280
She was gravely wounded

26:53.320 --> 26:54.640
and fading fast.

27:04.760 --> 27:06.360
Your spiritual veins will shatter,

27:06.880 --> 27:11.000
and the backlash will destroy you
after pouring your demon power into her.

27:29.040 --> 27:30.520
I only want her

27:31.320 --> 27:33.120
to stay alive

27:34.920 --> 27:36.160
and be happy.

27:58.840 --> 28:00.880
I grew up with Jian.

28:01.840 --> 28:03.360
Marrying her

28:03.880 --> 28:05.600
has always been my greatest wish.

28:07.200 --> 28:08.680
I'll take care of her

28:10.040 --> 28:11.360
for life,

28:11.960 --> 28:13.320
never leave her,

28:13.880 --> 28:15.240
never fail her.

28:17.280 --> 28:18.480
Don't worry.

28:19.440 --> 28:22.760
So Su Jian's fiancé
knew everything all along.

28:23.600 --> 28:25.520
Did Su Jian tell him?

28:27.680 --> 28:28.880
When you truly love someone,

28:30.160 --> 28:31.320
how can any secret stay hidden?

28:32.640 --> 28:34.240
Everything we saw

28:35.640 --> 28:37.160
was Jun's memory.

28:38.480 --> 28:45.160
FIFTY YEARS LATER

29:01.800 --> 29:03.560
I already know who the person in black is.

29:06.160 --> 29:07.080
<i>Iced treats.</i>

29:07.600 --> 29:09.040
<i>Opening up to each other.</i>

29:09.560 --> 29:11.560
-I will always be by your side.
-<i>Promising to stay together forever.</i>

29:12.680 --> 29:15.200
Those were your memories with Lu Wuyi.

29:15.960 --> 29:18.400
But now they're happening
between you and Su Jian.

29:20.000 --> 29:21.600
Maybe the memories in that painting

29:23.680 --> 29:24.800
are fake.

29:24.880 --> 29:26.000
True or false,

29:26.080 --> 29:27.680
we'll find out once we ask Han Ba.

29:30.000 --> 29:31.720
But I'd rather believe

29:32.360 --> 29:34.560
your story with Lu Wuyi

29:34.640 --> 29:36.240
was fabricated by Jiu Ying.

29:37.200 --> 29:38.840
Not just the memories,

29:39.480 --> 29:41.280
even Lu Wuyi herself

29:42.160 --> 29:43.720
may have been made up.

29:46.280 --> 29:48.320
<i>She stole the manuscript</i>

29:50.000 --> 29:52.440
<i>because she didn't want you</i>
<i>to find out the truth.</i>

29:53.320 --> 29:55.200
But Ji Ling said they were together.

29:56.920 --> 29:58.600
Ji Ling is defending her.

30:12.200 --> 30:15.000
Wu, I know it's you.

30:15.600 --> 30:18.720
The only one who could withstand
Wu Shiguang and Han Ba's power

30:19.560 --> 30:20.640
is you.

30:21.680 --> 30:24.680
But they never attacked you before.

30:25.680 --> 30:28.080
When did you absorb their power?

30:28.160 --> 30:29.120
Wuyi.

30:29.840 --> 30:30.960
Wuyi.

30:32.720 --> 30:35.160
Ji, help me.

30:37.800 --> 30:39.040
I'm begging you.

30:45.040 --> 30:46.560
I didn't give you away to Wu Wangyan.

30:47.160 --> 30:48.480
So, will you tell me

30:49.320 --> 30:50.880
what's really going on?

30:53.480 --> 30:54.800
Wu.

31:03.040 --> 31:04.080
Wu.

31:05.440 --> 31:07.200
Tell me the truth.

31:29.200 --> 31:30.280
Backlash…

31:32.080 --> 31:32.920
Your Word Magic

31:33.720 --> 31:35.440
is stronger than Xiaowei's?

31:37.120 --> 31:38.080
Wu,

31:39.080 --> 31:41.480
what happened to you?

31:42.320 --> 31:44.760
Why did you use Word Magic on Mu Long?

31:54.000 --> 31:55.920
Why did you take those manuscript pages?

31:57.840 --> 31:58.960
If you won't speak,

32:00.200 --> 32:01.240
I'll ask Wu Wangyan.

32:02.400 --> 32:03.640
Don't!

32:15.720 --> 32:17.120
Those pages

32:21.320 --> 32:22.320
contain a secret

32:23.040 --> 32:25.160
I never wanted Wangyan to know.

32:27.760 --> 32:29.920
I would lose her.

32:32.880 --> 32:34.040
What secret?

32:39.120 --> 32:41.360
I'm not a fox from the Formless Moon Sect.

32:46.760 --> 32:48.160
I'm not even

32:51.480 --> 32:53.040
a demon.

32:55.000 --> 32:56.520
I'm a monster.

32:59.680 --> 33:02.280
I'm a piece of trash

33:05.920 --> 33:06.760
stitched together by Jiu Ying.

33:09.520 --> 33:11.400
<i>I learned that all my memories</i>

33:11.480 --> 33:14.400
<i>are fake from Mu Long's story.</i>

33:17.720 --> 33:18.760
<i>So,</i>

33:19.840 --> 33:21.920
<i>I went to confront Jiu Ying.</i>

33:23.080 --> 33:25.400
Jiu Ying, come out.

33:36.400 --> 33:37.680
Why

33:38.560 --> 33:40.840
do my memories with Wangyan

33:40.920 --> 33:43.000
appear in Mu Long's story?

33:44.720 --> 33:45.800
Why

33:46.720 --> 33:49.040
are Little Pomegranate
and Wangyan's stories

33:49.720 --> 33:52.240
exactly the same as mine?

33:54.200 --> 33:55.360
Just why?

33:57.680 --> 33:59.400
What did you do

34:00.440 --> 34:02.400
to my memories?

34:24.800 --> 34:27.719
<i>When the Formless Moon Sect</i>
<i>attacked the flood dragons,</i>

34:28.239 --> 34:31.880
they fell into the trap of Xie Lingxi
and were completely wiped out.

34:35.120 --> 34:36.679
Before they were reborn,

34:37.280 --> 34:39.400
Jiu Ying took a part

34:40.440 --> 34:42.800
from each of their bodies,

34:43.520 --> 34:45.159
flesh, veins, spirit, or qi,

34:47.040 --> 34:48.239
and stitched them together

34:50.199 --> 34:51.600
to create me.

34:56.320 --> 34:59.120
And what she took from Wangyan

35:02.520 --> 35:03.760
was her heart.

35:05.200 --> 35:06.200
What about you?

35:10.120 --> 35:11.240
Where is your heart?

35:14.320 --> 35:15.480
That explains

35:17.080 --> 35:18.720
why Wu Wangyan dotes on you so much.

35:21.280 --> 35:22.320
That's because

35:23.800 --> 35:24.800
you are her heart.

35:28.920 --> 35:33.120
But Jiu Ying placed a spirit fragment
in her heart.

35:41.840 --> 35:44.400
The last fragment
you've been searching for

35:49.480 --> 35:50.600
is with me.

36:14.800 --> 36:15.840
I knew it all along.

36:20.560 --> 36:21.760
I just

36:23.360 --> 36:24.920
didn't understand

36:27.160 --> 36:29.360
why you stayed by my side,

36:31.240 --> 36:33.360
yet I couldn't sense that last fragment.

36:34.640 --> 36:35.640
Turns out

36:36.640 --> 36:38.920
it was hidden in Wangyan's heart.

36:39.960 --> 36:41.360
Her heart

36:43.480 --> 36:44.960
has always been protecting you.

36:46.400 --> 36:47.520
Wangyan's heart…

36:50.080 --> 36:53.640
When our hearts come into this world,

36:54.480 --> 36:55.560
one way or another,

36:56.320 --> 36:58.440
they are bound to be marked by love.

36:59.920 --> 37:01.080
Love

37:02.000 --> 37:05.080
is the oldest

37:06.560 --> 37:08.440
and the most powerful spell of all.

37:12.840 --> 37:15.640
Before any of us were revived, Jiu Ying

37:16.840 --> 37:18.840
altered our memories.

37:25.000 --> 37:26.120
<i>Wangyan.</i>

37:26.960 --> 37:28.680
<i>Wangyan, you made iced treats again.</i>

38:02.840 --> 38:04.000
Wangyan.

38:04.600 --> 38:05.680
Let's go.

38:12.240 --> 38:14.120
<i>You always manage to find me.</i>

38:14.200 --> 38:15.880
<i>You always hide in the dark.</i>

38:15.960 --> 38:18.480
Of course no one else can see you.

38:19.360 --> 38:20.640
But I can.

38:21.400 --> 38:22.440
My heart

38:22.960 --> 38:24.520
can feel you're here.

38:46.520 --> 38:48.720
Xie Lingxi killed all of you.

38:49.240 --> 38:50.480
But he didn't know

38:50.560 --> 38:52.280
the Power of the Moon

38:52.800 --> 38:54.080
is eternal.

39:05.560 --> 39:07.240
<i>When everyone was reborn,</i>

39:07.760 --> 39:11.560
<i>they took those altered memories as truth.</i>

39:12.960 --> 39:15.080
They believed they had
a younger sister like me.

39:21.080 --> 39:24.200
I used to think I was the new moon,

39:25.240 --> 39:26.880
one of the moon phases.

39:28.640 --> 39:30.280
But in the end,

39:34.560 --> 39:36.040
I was never real.

39:39.600 --> 39:42.000
I'm nothing but a shameless thief.

39:44.360 --> 39:46.480
I stole their memories

39:48.120 --> 39:49.360
to piece together a life of my own.

39:53.920 --> 39:54.840
Full moon,

39:56.760 --> 39:57.600
waning gibbous,

39:58.440 --> 39:59.320
last-quarter,

40:01.080 --> 40:01.960
waxing gibbous,

40:02.760 --> 40:03.800
first-quarter,

40:04.840 --> 40:05.840
waning crescent,

40:06.880 --> 40:07.840
and waxing crescent.

40:09.320 --> 40:10.640
In the sky,

40:15.240 --> 40:17.360
there was never a place for me.

40:39.680 --> 40:40.920
Your place

40:42.640 --> 40:43.920
was never in the sky.

40:46.880 --> 40:48.280
It's in my heart.

40:54.640 --> 40:56.560
Nothing between us

40:57.720 --> 40:59.480
is fake.

41:00.600 --> 41:02.640
From the day we met,

41:04.880 --> 41:07.640
every moment this world has witnessed

41:10.240 --> 41:12.360
belongs only to us.

41:46.240 --> 41:48.800
But how did Wuyi come to know all this?

41:50.720 --> 41:52.840
She arrived at the inn
at the same time as us.

41:53.760 --> 41:55.480
How did you learn

41:56.760 --> 41:58.400
the truth?

42:01.880 --> 42:03.240
Maybe

42:04.920 --> 42:07.120
Lu Wuyi went through something
we don't know about.

42:11.200 --> 42:12.240
Wu,

42:13.840 --> 42:14.960
tell me.

42:16.280 --> 42:17.800
No matter what happens,

42:19.000 --> 42:21.320
I'll face it with you.

42:24.920 --> 42:27.680
This isn't the first time
I've been through this.

42:28.840 --> 42:30.200
The Chatter Inn.

42:31.400 --> 42:32.720
This drought.

42:33.960 --> 42:35.400
It's not the first time,

42:36.520 --> 42:37.880
not the tenth,

42:39.360 --> 42:41.040
but countless times.

42:55.360 --> 42:56.920
<i>From the moment we entered the inn,</i>

42:57.000 --> 42:58.560
<i>at the Zi hour that night,</i>

42:59.080 --> 43:00.640
<i>I've been trapped in a loop,</i>

43:01.600 --> 43:03.480
reliving it over and over again.

43:06.800 --> 43:13.440
FIRST REWIND

43:54.000 --> 43:57.200
Big drumstick…

43:59.000 --> 44:00.080
Miss Mu.

44:01.880 --> 44:03.720
-Miss Mu.
-What are you trying to do?

44:03.800 --> 44:06.880
You… You've stained my manuscript.

44:45.640 --> 44:48.080
I've relived everything again and again.

44:48.840 --> 44:50.600
I've endured countless attacks
from Han Ba,

44:50.680 --> 44:51.880
Wu Shiguang,

44:51.960 --> 44:54.280
and Li Jie.

44:54.360 --> 44:57.160
That's why none of their spells
can harm me.

44:57.800 --> 44:59.440
And my Word Magic

45:00.320 --> 45:01.400
has surpassed yours.

45:04.200 --> 45:05.840
Time reversal?

45:07.640 --> 45:09.600
How could Jiu Ying possess such power?

45:12.000 --> 45:13.240
I don't know.

45:19.640 --> 45:21.120
Time reversal

45:21.760 --> 45:25.040
damages the body, doesn't it?

45:26.520 --> 45:27.440
Yes.

45:29.320 --> 45:31.160
And the toll only gets worse each time.

45:35.800 --> 45:39.360
So Ji, help me.

45:41.400 --> 45:42.480
I'm afraid.

45:43.240 --> 45:45.280
I'm afraid that once
Wangyan finds out the truth,

45:45.800 --> 45:46.960
she'll hate me.

45:48.040 --> 45:50.000
I don't want to lose her.

45:51.200 --> 45:52.160
Don't be afraid.

45:53.240 --> 45:55.000
You stole the manuscript

45:55.960 --> 45:57.880
and used Word Magic on Mu Long.

45:58.800 --> 46:00.200
Wangyan will never find out what happened.

46:04.080 --> 46:04.960
No.

46:05.760 --> 46:07.280
There's another way.

46:09.200 --> 46:10.920
All the truth and memories

46:11.000 --> 46:13.120
are stored inside Mu Long's horn pendant.

46:13.720 --> 46:15.480
Every time time reverses,

46:16.040 --> 46:19.280
I can't stop Wangyan
from discovering what's inside.

46:20.120 --> 46:21.360
Maybe

46:23.000 --> 46:25.640
that's why I'm trapped here.

46:27.480 --> 46:29.880
My fear of losing her

46:31.800 --> 46:33.440
has bound me to this place.

46:36.400 --> 46:37.680
But this time,

46:39.400 --> 46:41.080
I know the truth.

46:42.200 --> 46:43.800
Maybe this is fate.

46:44.960 --> 46:47.400
It's giving me a chance
to change everything for you.

46:51.280 --> 46:52.560
You're willing to help me?

46:56.720 --> 46:59.000
I would do anything for you.

47:02.960 --> 47:05.280
Take that pendant back for me.

47:06.600 --> 47:07.640
Help me.
